metadata.name: The Cave - Chapter 5: Mythscapes
metadata.description:
Mythscapes is a fairytale collaboration between two outstandingly talented artists, SafetyFirst and Bstract. With its bold textured backgrounds and etching-like figures evading the clutches of nightmarish skeletal monsters, it suggests an epic quest in a dreamlike abstract realm.  Mythscapes evokes stories passed down through generations, where the context drops away and only the archetypes remain. Mythscapes hints at a fable, a foundational allegory, about the way our collective memory is built on the stories we tell each other.

SafetyFirst: https://foundation.app/@yosafetyfirst  
Bstract: https://foundation.app/@BstractArt
